  (text "AUX RAILS: VBUS 12-30V -> LMR36015 (60V, 400kHz, adj) -> 5V0 -> NCP1117 -> 3V3.\nFB divider 100K/24.9K -> 5.016V (VREF=1.0V). NC pin ties to SW per datasheet.\nLayout: CIN loop tight; BOOT cap adjacent; VCC LDO cap 1uF, no external loads." (at 33.02 40.64 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 4d36a705-ba7d-4810-b3f6-2bb500bcd2ed))
